    "body": "## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Have a fresh install.\r\n2. Launch Firefox Focus.\r\n3. Rotate the device in Landscape mode.\r\n4. Switch between the onboarding tour tips and observe the transition.\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\nThe transition should be smooth.\r\n### Actual behavior\r\nThe transition is not done smoothly, the previous tip is partially displayed on the left side of the screen when switching tips.\r\nThe issue is more visible in Landscape mode, but it is also noticeable in Portrait mode.\r\n### Device information\r\n\r\n* Android device: Google Pixel 6 (Android 12).\r\n* Focus version: 97.0.0-beta.1, RC 96.1.1.\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/89388888/149170242-57b3b482-871b-4131-8668-11ae2e599133.mp4\r\n",
